{"tid":2059064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#ShutDownSTEM 只係Last 1日嘅活動嚟 唔係持續停止科學研究","createTime":"2020-06-10T15:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T02:39:19.000Z","uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f26ea02245eb41e00231e96beb0465e3e1d77f1e","tid":2059064,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"詳情：<a href=\"https://www.shutdownstem.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutdownstem.com%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=4c91b9eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shutdownstem.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔離Po個Topic都幾誤導<br />\nNature唔係叫人永久停止科學研究 只係停一日半日<br />\n叫人用一日嚟反思下<br />\n佢地Science Can Wait<br />\n<br />\n吹到世界文明大倒退 唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如欣賞下人地搞罷工罷學 係啲教授、科研機構由上而下咁罷<br />\n今日唔上堂 堂課唔洗交 課遲啲再補返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自然》雜誌：呼籲停止科學研究，一起思考如何為黑人科學家爭取權益<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058830\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058830</a>"},{"pid":"883d813101553814d77f2198cd0f5c8d97059183","tid":2059064,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"本來都幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【墨落無悔 堅定抗爭】 11個初選要留意嘅攬炒派蒲頭啦!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7bd60b782439124f05cef2cab1d270fd8906553","tid":2059064,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"shut down個意義係邊?"},{"pid":"a0e78c4066116472a444eb2e9b18bf31d326e71b","tid":2059064,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f7bd60b782439124f05cef2cab1d270fd8906553","tid":2059064,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"shut down個意義係邊?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"#Shu